  "Description": {
    "English": "As the boundaries of reality begin to weaken, the risk of <span class=\"name name-special\">catastrophic breach anomalies</span> increases.<br><br>This device monitors and maintains the local <span class=\"name name-technology\">boundary strength</span>, guarding against reality continuity errors. Supply the device with <span class=\"name name-special\">glass</span> to maintain functionality.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "随着现实的边界不断崩塌，发生<span class=\"name name-special\">灾难性裂隙异象</span>的威胁正在不断扩大。<br><br>这种设备能够监控并维护本地的<span class=\"name name-technology\">边界强度</span>，同时抵御现实连续体的崩坏。为装置提供<span class=\"name name-special\">玻璃</span>以确保其能够持续运作。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "隨著現實邊界開始變得脆弱，<span class=\"name name-special\">災難性異常裂痕</span>出現機率提升。<br><br>這個裝置能監控並維持局部<span class=\"name name-technology\">邊界強度</span>，以防現實連續性發生錯誤。補充<span class=\"name name-special\">玻璃</span>便能使該裝置正常運作。"
  },
